title: Man Arrested On Child Pornography Charges In Sioux Falls
text:
Man Arrested On Child Pornography Charges In Sioux Falls October 22, 2015, 4:03 PM SIOUX FALLS, SD - 
A Sioux Falls man faces child pornography charges after a search recovered pornographic material. 
Authorities arrested 35-year-old Collin Utterback Thursday in connection to an investigation of child pornography being distributed from Sioux Falls out of state. 
A search by the Internet Crimes Against Children Task Force found several videos of child pornography in Utterback's possession. Utterback later admitted that he had taken other pornographic photographs and distributed them to people over the internet. 
Utterback is charged with 5 counts of Manufacturing, Distribution, or Possession of Child Pornography. Â© 2015 KELOLAND TV. All Rights Reserved.
